title: Tauck announces various new options in road maps for their 2016 brochure
text:
Tauck announces various new options in road maps for their 2016 brochure Original, timely global, travel, tourism, business news and research: 
Oct 05, 2015 eTN Exclusive: Unique and original, timely, global breaking news: 
Tauck’s “Yellow Roads of Europe” land tours - 35 exclusive journeys following the scenic routes marked in yellow on Michelin road maps - are now available in a new UK brochure for 2016. 
Each of Tauck’s 35 Yellow Roads European land tours is contained in a new 136-page brochure (which will be published w/c 12 October) and on the European section of Tauck’s website.
